Imp Points of Interface


Interface = 100% abstraction ka primary tool (traditionally).
Interface ka object nahi ban sakta.
Interface methods by default public abstract hote hain.
Interface variables by default public static final hote hain.
Interface constructor nahi hota.
Class multiple interfaces implement kar sakti hai.
Interface interface ko extends karta hai.
Java 8 se default aur static methods allowed hain.
Java 9 se private methods bhi allowed hain.
